</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">loukaye</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">9 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Create a category or an entire data base tracking  every corporate or individual donation or gift that has been returned to a donor or regifted to a charitable organization from congressionals (Senate and House). Record date of receipt and date of rejection, amount and reason why the donation was not admitted. Of course the release of this information would have to be powered by the public servant, but it may prove irresistable to some to set the standard for not accepting corporate cash. </div>
