<div id="Idea_2756"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2756-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2756">Allow public to requests for documents & data to be routinely accessible, require agency response&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3967-4049">Sunshine in Government Initiative </a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">9 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Each agency should allow the public to request that information be made routinely available to the public, and that request should obligate the agency to respond.  </div>
