<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2686">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2686', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2686&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 277</div><div>Votes Against : 25</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2686'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2686" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 277</div><div>Votes Against : 25</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2686'))">252</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2686', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2686&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
</div>
</td>
<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2686"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2686-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2686">There is No Reason Why CRS Reports Should Not be Public&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">sylvester_ron</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The Congressional Research Service does some excellent research and analysis on all manner of things.  These reports are not officially accessible to taxpayers.<br/><br/>CRS reports to Congress or individual members of Congress should be readily accessible via the World Wide Web within two weeks of their delivery to the requesting member(s).</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2686" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2686', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=2686')">Comments (6)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2686"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=congressional research service">congressional research service</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2686"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2662">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2662">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2662', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2662&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 21</div><div>Votes Against : 66</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2662'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2662" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 21</div><div>Votes Against : 66</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2662'))">-45</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2662', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2662&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
</div>
</td>
<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2662"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2662-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2662">Create a New Cable Channel Devoted to Delivering News and Information About the Government&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">kfitzmorgan</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">I suggest that the government create a cable TV channel that broadcasts news and information about the government 24/7.  I don’t mean a single program – I mean an entire channel devoted to information about our government. The programming would be exciting and interesting. It could feature:<br/><br/>- breaking news<br/>- daily news<br/>- call-in programs<br/>- a series on a particular topic<br/>- some private programs, like Ken Burns' documentary about the Civil War<br/>- the president's weekly address<br/>- guest speakers from different areas of the government <br/>- late night talk shows<br/>- programming slots devoted to the different branches of government <br/>- shows for kids<br/>- educational programs<br/><br/>It would have to be staffed and run by experienced private-sector people. It would have to be engaging and fun, as well as informative. That's achievable when you have multiple programs, not just one, like the President's weekly address. <br/><br/>The government could pass legislation saying that all cable channels must carry this station for free, uninterrupted. There is existing legislation governing the cable companies, so there is precedent.<br/></div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2662" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2662', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=2662')">Comments (8)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2662"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=cable tv news channel tv television talk show tv program access weekly address c-span computer ipod podcast web sitecnn npr public radio">cable tv news channel tv television talk show tv program access weekly address c-span computer ipod podcast web sitecnn npr public radio</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2662"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2643">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2643">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2643', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2643&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 196</div><div>Votes Against : 40</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2643'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2643" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 196</div><div>Votes Against : 40</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2643'))">156</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2643', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2643&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
</div>
</td>
<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2643"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2643-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2643">Use Visual recording and mini animations to convey complex ideas&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">nancycreates</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The use of words and images work well to convey complex ideas. This process is called visual recording. I used this process for the Cabinet retreat during President Clinton's second term and have posted samples (now unclassified) visuals at http://www.visualrecording.blogspot.com<br/>Many skilled visual recorders are available across the country to translate ideas into images and words and others can be trained in this skill as well. Upon request I can provide sample animations that are made in a day and convey complex concepts.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2643" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2643', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=2643')">Comments (20)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2643"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=visual recording">visual recording</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=animation">animation</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2643"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2630">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2630">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2630', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2630&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 278</div><div>Votes Against : 31</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2630'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2630" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 278</div><div>Votes Against : 31</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2630'))">247</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2630', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2630&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
</div>
